DESCRIPTION:UPDATE: location for the in-person meeting is the Lounge @ Klø
 fta (where the bookshelves are\, next to the kitchenette)\n\n\nHello Every
 one\,\n\nThanks to a strong basis and joint efforts\, we're ready to say o
 ut loud: the Design System is ready!\n\nBut what does this mean? Is this v
 ersion 1.0 or 2.0? What does it include\, how does it enable us to deliver
  faster? What jobs had to be done to reach this phase? How did we work tog
 ether? What's new? To understand from where we got here\, and to answer th
 ese questions\, we're preparing a little presentation and a little surpris
 e.\n\nJoin us and celebrate together on the 4th September (Thursday) in th
 e Kløfta office after lunch.\nImportant: if you're planning to join in pe
 rson in Kløfta\, please let us know until 22nd August 2025 (this Friday) 
 12:00 (after lunch) the latest. (Just hit “reply” (NOT “reply all”
 !) and tell me if you’re joining.)\n\nWith warm regards\,\nUX team\n\n__
