DESCRIPTION:Hi all\,\n\n\n\nYou are invited to join our upcoming R&D-wide d
 emo where the Americas R&D team will present unit sortation in eController
 .\n\nThe demos are mainly aimed at developers and will go show some techni
 cal details. The session will be recorded for those unable to attend live.
 \n\nWe will demonstrate -\n\n  *\nData into ESS ItmSort\n  *\nWave Start\n
   *\nScan On Fly\n  *\nWave Stop\n  *\nClose Carton\n  *\nSort Results\n\n
