DESCRIPTION:Hi all\,\n\nYou are invited to join our upcoming R&D-wide demo 
 where the Common Services teams will present several key components in ESF
 .\nThe demos are mainly aimed at developers and will go show some technica
 l details. The session will be recorded for those unable to attend live.\n
 \nAgenda\n\nIdentity & Access Management (IAM)\n\n  *   Introduction to IA
 M/Keycloak and its capabilities\n  *   User Management Portal (UMP)\n  *  
  Client Library\n\nLogging & Monitoring (L&M)\n\n  *   Logs from Test Cent
 er (eManager\, eController and eOperator)\n  *   Dashboard for eManager\n 
  *   Metrics\n\nPII Service\n\n  *   Overview of the PII Service\n  *   En
 d-to-End flow from eHub into PII and token handling incl. scheduled deleti
 on\n\nConfiguration Manager\n\n  *   Overview of Configuration Manager\n  
 *   Client Library\n\n\nWe hope you’ll join us to learn more about these
  building blocks and how they fit into ESS.\n\n___________________________
