DESCRIPTION:Hello everyone\,\n\nwe invite you to the technical deep dive to
  AXON\, the Element Logic Design System. (Please note that this is an open
  invitation\, you can decide if you want to join\, and of course\, there w
 ill be recording.)\n\nThe UX team\, and especially Andre would like to exp
 lain\n- how components are built up\,\n- details about their properties an
 d variables\, and the interaction design prototypes\n- how we use the comp
 onents when creating designs\n- how designers can help developers when usi
 ng the components.\n\nWe believe that the demo should take max. 30 minutes
 \, while we have an additional 20 minutes set aside for Q&A.\n\nBest wishe
 s on behalf of the UX team\,\nDora\n\n____________________________________
