BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:\nHi everyone\,\n\nThis will be an online-only meeting. While i
 t’s challenging to accommodate all time zones perfectly\, we hope the ch
 osen time works reasonably well for everyone. Please note that the schedul
 e is based on Norwegian time.\n\nPreparations\nAll teams are expected to p
 repare a draft plan in Airfocus ahead of the ESS planning for Iteration 2 
 (covering the next three months).\nThis should include:\n\n  *   Milestone
 s\n  *   Opportunities\n  *   Epics\n  *   Risks and mitigations\nBacklog 
 owners and PMs have been informed and are responsible for coordinating thi
 s preparation with their teams.\n\nPractical information\n\n  *   This is 
 a fully online meeting. Please join individually—no hybrid setups.\n  * 
   Ensure you have food\, drinks\, and snacks ready. Breaks will be short.\
 n  *   Details about breakout sessions and online meeting rooms will be sh
 ared in advance.\n  *   Log in to airfocus<https://eur02.safelinks.protect
 ion.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Felementlogic.airfocus.com%2F&data=05%7C
 02%7C%7C260f9584c4f44c86752108ddf50aa7b1%7Cdbaef1534a3e40cd83cbc5e2e1c6a48
 a%7C0%7C0%7C638936148315892139%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnR
 ydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%
 7C0%7C%7C%7C&sdata=Ir49Yb61SZI5PE7jvqoGWxC1%2BsmqDeh7sDJsr7Zmi0o%3D&reserv
 ed=0> before the meeting and confirm you have access to a usable workspace
 .\nIf you need help or access (read/write)\, please reach out and specify 
 your needs.\n\nAgenda\nPlease note\, there might adjustments to the agenda
 .\n\nThe main goal is to detail the planning of epics for the next three m
 onths\, including timelines and dependencies across teams. Each epic shoul
 d be linked to a relevant opportunity and/or milestone. Teams should also 
 be ready to present an overview of current risks.\n\nStart time\nEnd time\
 nDuration\nTopic\nResponsible\n13:00\n13:20\n20 min\nWelcome - introductio
 n day 1 (common session)\n- Business context\n- Practical information\nChr
 istian Rognes\nAnne H. Pedersen\,\nGard Heiaas\n13:20\n13:25\n5 min\nBreak
 \n13:25\n14:25\n1 hour\nBreakout sessions part 1\n\n  *   Detail your team
 ’s backlog and handle dependencies between your team and other ESS teams
