DESCRIPTION:Hi all\,\nYou are invited to join our upcoming R&D-wide demo wh
 ere the RPP team will present the things they have been working on in ESS.
 \n\nThe demos are mainly aimed at developers and will go show some technic
 al details. The session will be recorded for those unable to attend live.\
 n\nMessage bus client .NET\n\n  *\nNew features and behavior\n  *\nHow to 
 do some troubleshooting of NATS\n  *\nUpcoming plan\n\nData Visualization 
 components\n\n  *\nIntroduction to design\n  *\nIntroduction to components
 \n  *\nHow to use in React & Blazor\n\nStock reservation service\n\n  *\nP
 urpose\,  use case and requirements\n  *\nHow we went about building it\n 
  *\nHow to use\n  *\nArchitecture of service\n\nWe hope you’ll join us t
 o learn more about these things and how they fit into ESS!\n\n\n\n\n______
