DESCRIPTION:Looking forward to seeing you all for the workshop tomorrow! He
 re is the agenda we’ve planned for this time. Those of you who don’t h
 ave presentations don’t need to do any particular preparations\, but I
 ’ve included the questions we’re going to ask you to comment on at the
  end of the workshop so you can have them in the back of your mind.\n\nWel
 come and expectations – Jon - 15 minutes\nRelease process and planning 
 – Jon - 15 minutes\nDeveloper testing and review – Chaminda - 25 minut
 es\n\nBreak - 5 minutes\n\nManual testing – Savithri - 20 minutes\nSpecF
 low testing – Savithri - 20 minutes\nSuggestions for testing changes –
  Leif – 20 minutes\n\nReflections from those who have not presented – 
 3 minutes each\n- Have we addressed any of the things you wanted to get ou
 t of this?\n- Has your perspective changed on anything?\n- What is the mos
 t important thing to do next?\n\nWrap up – Jon 5 minutes\n______________
