 the future control room?\n\nDTC\n\n  *   What even is it?\n  *   Does DTC 
 stand for Down to Code?\n\nOPC-UA and Visu\n\n  *   What are we doing as p
 art of the Control Room discovery\n  *   What will I see in the Klofta tes
 t center soon\n\n\nLook forward to seeing you all there!\n\n\n____________
