DESCRIPTION:Please forward to your team members\, if not already included\n
 \nEnd of October we want to demo the walking skeleton with putaway functio
 nality.\n\nWhere are we in respect to that goal and what do we need to foc
 us on to make that happen in production quality?\n\nPlease prepare:\n\n  *
    What dependencies do you have to reach that goal?\n  *   What risks do 
 you see?\n  *\nWhat focus should we have for the coming two weeks?\n\nFeel
  free to decide for yourself if you want to take part\, read the summary o
 r watch the recap. If you take part\, please be focused and dare to speak 
 up to bring attention to impediments or risks.\n\n---\nA "Team of Teams" m
 eeting is designed to facilitate communication and collaboration across mu
 ltiple teams within an organization.\nThe primary objectives are to share 
 updates\, align work\, provide feedback\, and ask questions.\nThese meetin
 gs enhance alignment and accountability\, ensuring that all teams are work
 ing towards common goals [1]<https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.co
 m/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dwhat%2Bis%2Ba%2Bteaam%2
