 Bfeedback%252C%2Band%2Bask%2Bquestions%252C%2Betc.%26oq%3Dwhat%2Bis%2Ba%2B
 teaam%2Bof%2Bteams%2Bmeeting%2Bfor%2Ban%2Barena%2Bto%2Bget%2Bupdates%2Bon%
 2Bwhat%2Bthe%2Bother%2Bteams%2Bare%2Bdoing%252C%2Bto%2Balign%2Bwork%252C%2
 Bgive%2Bfeedback%252C%2Band%2Bask%2Bquestions%252C%2Betc.%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZj
 aHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOdIBCTI4NDAyajBqN6gCALACAA%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-
 8%23sr-1&data=05%7C02%7C%7Cb2d30c4345224760cc4708de8a92034b%7Cdbaef1534a3e
 40cd83cbc5e2e1c6a48a%7C0%7C0%7C639100556909426043%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8
 eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbC
 IsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&sdata=yCKdxmHKWRVnC5A7YLdiHFKBlferdbhSNJDB
 PhisiHY%3D&reserved=0>.\nEffective meetings should be well-planned\, time-
