DESCRIPTION:Hi\, everyone\nGoal:\nShowcase progress from version 0.3 by dem
 onstrating working software and the business value delivered\, gather feed
 back\, and foster transparency around ELWS development.\nAgenda:\n1.    Pr
 esentation of completed features in version v.3\n2.    Live demonstration 
 of key functionality : Picking with deviation handling and inspection\n3. 
    Open floor for feedback and discussion\nFor the employees in Stuttgart:
  Hope many of you will meet in the test center at the Stuttgart office.\nK
 ind regards\n\nVennlig hilsen / Best regards\,\n\nAnne Helga Mathsen Peder
