 ime to talk.\nPlease tell me if there are any agenda points you would like
  to add on a regular basis.\n\nAreas we can/will touch upon are:\n\n  *   
 How are you?\n  *   Any challenges we should discuss?\n  *   Priorities\n 
  *   Workload\n  *   What motivates you?\n  *   Anything you think it is i
 mportant that we prioritize?\n  *   Feedback to me?\n  *   Anything I can 
 help you with?\n  *   Etc\n\nKind regards\nAnne Helga\n\n_________________
