DESCRIPTION:Hi everyone\,\n\nThis will be a fully online planning session. 
 Please note that all times are in Norwegian time (CET).\n\nPreparations\nA
 ll teams are expected to prepare a draft plan in Jira ahead of the ELWS Pl
 anning for Iteration 4 (Kidsworld 0.5 scope/ the next two months).\nBacklo
 g Owners and PMs have already been informed and are responsible for coordi
 nating this preparation with their teams.\nThe expectation is that teams c
 ome prepared with a structured\, review-ready plan.\n\nPractical informati
 on\n\n  *   This is a fully online meeting. Please join individually – n
 o hybrid setups.\n  *   Make sure you have food\, drinks\, and snacks avai
 lable\, as breaks will be short.\n  *   Breakout sessions and online meeti
 ng room details will be shared in advance.\n\nAgenda\nThe main objective i
 s to align on dependencies\, timelines\, and risks\, and to agree on and c
 ommit to a realistic plan for the Kidsworld 0.5 scope / the next two month
 s.\n\nEach team is expected to present their planning\, covering:\n\n  *  
  Epics (in Jira Plans)\n  *   Key dependencies on other teams (in Jira Pla
 ns)\n  *   Main risks (in AirFocus – PMs have access\; please reach out 
 if support is needed)\n  *   Confidence rating (given live during the sess
 ion)\n\nBreakout sessions\nLink to the schedule of the breakout session an
 d where you add topics for risk meetings: ELWS breakout seessions planning
  itereation 4.xlsx<https://elementlogic.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/sites/RD/Shar
