 s.\n\nStart time\nEnd time\nDuration\nTopic\nResponsible\n13:00\n13:15\n15
  min\nWelcome - introduction to day 1 (common session)\n\n  *   Business c
 ontext\n  *   Practical information\nChristian Rognes\nAnne H. Pedersen\,\
 nGard Heiaas\n13:15\n13:25\n10 min\nVisual presentation of ELWS (common se
 ssion)\n\n  *   UX prototype\nDora Makszy\n13:25\n13:55\n30 min\nPresentat
 ion of Roadmap (common session)\n\n  *   Opportunities for iteration 4 (in
