DESCRIPTION:From the AI champions guild we want to inform you about what we
  learned\, what we found useful and how you can apply it to your daily wor
 k.\n\nSo join if any of the following sound interesting to you\, you have 
 a specific question about AI usage or just want to stay in the loop about 
 AI.\n\nThe rough agenda will be:\n\n  *\n(Live-)Demo of spec-driven develo
 pment (using qrisp)\n  *\nMiro AI\n  *\nGitHub instructions collection rep
 o and how to integrate in your own repo\n  *\nRequesting AI tools you want
  to use\n\n\nThere will be also be an option for you to ask any questions 
 you might have. If we don't have the answer for something\, we'll take it 
 as a research-request  and get back to you.\n\nIf you or your team feel li
 ke you could benefit from a more in-depth sparring session on how you spec
 ifically can apply AI\, feel free to reach out in our Slack channel or me 
 personally.\n\nThe goal of the AI champions guild is to help all of you ma
 ke the most of the AI tools available\, so don't hesitate to reach out.\n\
