DESCRIPTION:Hi\,\n\nGot a new meeting at the same time. Hope it is Ok to mo
 ve it.\n\nKind regards\nAnne Helga\n\n\nHi\,\n\nI suggest we have regular 
 meetings where we have some time to talk.\nPlease tell me if there are any
  agenda points you would like to add on a regular basis.\n\nAreas we can/w
 ill touch upon are:\n\n  *   How are you?\n  *   Any challenges we should 
 discuss?\n  *   Priorities\n  *   Workload\n  *   What motivates you?\n  *
    Anything you think it is important that we prioritize?\n  *   Feedback 
 to me?\n  *   Anything I can help you with?\n  *   Etc\n\nKind regards\nAn
 ne Helga\n\n______________________________________________________________
