DESCRIPTION:Update:\n\nAs part of the introduction\, we’d like you to ans
 wer the following questions about yourself:\n\n•What is your role in the
  team?\n•How long have you been part of the eManager/eOperator journey?\
 n•What contributions do you make beyond your formal job description?\n
 •What is your favorite hobby?\n\n\nHi.\n\nThe eManager developers are vi
 siting from Sri Lanka. This is an optional chance to put a face to a Jira 
 user. We’ll do a round of introductions and then open the floor to a dis
 cussion about how we can work together even better.\n\nThis will be an in-
 person only meeting. If you can’t make it at this time but have somethin
 g you want to discuss with the team while they are here\, please contact m
 e. The team is here until Friday the 24th and we have some room in the age
 nda for additional discussions.\n
