 rom Tiqri.\n\nOur plan is to walk along Akerselva from Nydalen to Schous p
 lass\, followed by dinner at Popolare (https://www.popolare.no/). If the w
 eather doesn’t cooperate\, we’ll arrange an alternative plan or meet d
 irectly for dinner.\n\nPlease reply today. If you have any dietary restric
 tions\, let me know when you respond to the invitation.\n\nHope you can jo
 in us!😊\n\nKind regards\nJon and Anne Helga\n\n________________________
