DESCRIPTION:From the AI champions guild we want to inform you about what we
  learned\, what we found useful and how you can apply it to your daily wor
 k.\n\nSo join if any of the following sound interesting to you\, you have 
 a specific question about AI usage or just want to stay in the loop about 
 AI.\n\nThe agenda will be presented shortly before the meeting.\n\nIf you 
 or your team feel like you could benefit from a more in-depth sparring ses
 sion on how you specifically can apply AI\, feel free to reach out in our 
 Slack channel or to me directly.\n\nThe goal of the AI champions guild is 
