DESCRIPTION:We need to move the meeting by one week. I'm on vacation and ne
 xt week we can share some insights into the currently ongoing AI-work as w
 ell.\n\nSorry for the short notice.\n\n\n\nFrom the AI champions guild we 
 want to inform you about what we learned\, what we found useful and how yo
 u can apply it to your daily work.\n\nSo join if any of the following soun
 d interesting to you\, you have a specific question about AI usage or just
  want to stay in the loop about AI.\n\nThe agenda will be presented shortl
 y before the meeting.\n\nIf you or your team feel like you could benefit f
 rom a more in-depth sparring session on how you specifically can apply AI\
 , feel free to reach out in our Slack channel or to me directly.\n\nThe go
 al of the AI champions guild is to help all of you make the most of the AI
  tools available\, so don't hesitate to reach out.\n\nSlack Channel: #ai-c
